          <p class="text-gray-700">Both support e-commerce but neither is a dedicated e-commerce platform. Framer: Gumroad/Snipcart integration. Mixo: Stripe integration. For serious online stores, look elsewhere (10Web, Durable with WooCommerce).</p>
